Package: dockpipe
Version: 0.4.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, docker.io | docker-ce
Maintainer: dockpipe maintainers
Description: Run, isolate, and act — pipe commands into disposable containers
 dockpipe is a primitive: spawn container, run command/script inside it,
 perform an optional action on the result. Agent-agnostic and
 command-agnostic. Use for one-off commands, CI-like runs, or AI tools.
